Definition: Greek mythology) a handsome youth loved by both Aphrodite and Persephone
Example: when Adonis died Zeus decreed that he should spend winters in the underworld with Persephone and spend summers with Aphrodite
Synonyms: daemon, noun, group, Greek_mythology, c, Greek, mythology, a, handsome, youth, loved, by, both, Aphrodite, and, Persephone, when, died, Zeus, decreed, that, he, should, spend, winters, in, the, underworld, with, summers
Category: noun.person
